data.description: Discover tranquility in Haskins! 3-bed, 2.5bath home is nestled in a serene subdivision. Boasting 1812 sf, residence welcomes you w spacious fam rm adorned by cozy gas fireplace. Eat-in kitchen is a culinary haven, feat sliding glass door leading to charming backyard patio. Full bsmt holds endless possibilities. Built in 2005, home exudes modern charm w new carpet, fresh paint, & upgraded appliances. Convenience meets style w 2-car garage & newer A/C unit. The only residential listing in Haskins, rare opportunity to embrace comfort & elegance in this peaceful community. Your dream home awaits!
